# BB Website — Project Context

Law firm website for Bárbara Barbizani. Next.js 14 (Pages Router), React 18, bilingual (pt/en).

## Stack & Structure

- **Styling:** Tailwind + SASS. Colors: `blue` (#1E2E45), `gold` (#B19460), `dark` (#2f333a). Background: #e8e9e1.
- **Fonts:** DM Serif Display (headings, buttons), DM Sans (body, nav), Encode Sans (hero subtitle). Loaded in `src/styles/fonts.js`, injected via CSS vars in `_app.js`.
- **i18n:** `next-intl` with `pt` (default) and `en`. Strings in `src/messages/{locale}.json`. Arrays accessed via `useTranslation()` → `getTranslationsArray(key)`. Never hardcode visible text.
- **Animations:** `<Animated type="fade|slide|slide-in-left|slide-in-right|scale-up" />` using `@react-spring/web` + `useInView`. Trigger once on scroll.
- **Path alias:** `@/` → `src/`.
- **Forms:** Formspree via `@formspree/react`.
- **SEO:** `next-seo` in `AppHead.jsx`, `next-sitemap` in postbuild.

## Key Directories

- `src/pages/` — Routes (index, about, contacts, practice-areas, 404)
- `src/components/` — Layout, Navbar, Footer, HeroSection, Button, Card, Form, Animated, etc.
- `src/messages/` — `pt.json`, `en.json`
- `src/hooks/` — `useTranslation.jsx`, `useIsMobile.jsx`
- `__tests__/` — Jest + Testing Library. Mocks in `jest.setup.js`. Helpers in `__tests__/__utils__/`.

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` — dev server
- `pnpm build` — production build (+ sitemap)
- `pnpm test` — all tests
- `pnpm test:smoke` — dependency smoke tests
